{
  "scenes": [
    {
      "sceneKey": "start",
      "content": {
        "bg": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-15187092688054-9e50e2af4f1a?w=1920",
        "text": "指挥官，欢迎来到铁锈战争的战场！\n这里是前线指挥部，敌军正在集结，我们需要你的指挥才能取得胜利。",
        "characters": [
          {
            "name": "基础机甲",
            "image": "/uploads/images/scenes/characters/47982733-a03a-473a-8628-dcfec368a1a6.png",
            "position": "center"
          }
        ],
        "options": [
          {
            "text": "了解当前战况",
            "next": "briefing"
          },
          {
            "text": "直接开始战斗",
            "next": "battle_start"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "sceneKey": "briefing",
      "content": {
        "bg": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1451187580459-43490279c0fa?w=1920",
        "text": "基础机甲：'报告指挥官！目前我方基地位于东部高地，敌军主力正在西面集结。'\n基础机甲：'根据侦察，敌军拥有大量装甲单位，我们需要做好充分准备。'",
        "characters": [
          {
            "name": "基础机甲",
            "image": "/uploads/images/scenes/characters/47982733-a03a-473a-8628-dcfec368a1a6.png",
            "position": "left"
          }
        ],
        "options": [
          {
            "text": "我方有哪些单位可用？",
            "next": "units_intro"
          },
          {
            "text": "直接部署防御",
            "next": "defense_deploy"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "sceneKey": "units_intro",
      "content": {
        "bg": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1451187580459-43490279c0fa?w=1920",
        "text": "基础机甲：'报告指挥官！目前我方可调动的作战单位如下：'\n基础机甲：'重型坦克小姐 - 地面主力，火力强大但机动性一般。'\n基础机甲：'猛犸坦克小姐 - 重装单位，双管火炮，防御力极高。'\n基础机甲：'等离子坦克小姐 - 高科技单位，等离子武器威力惊人。'\n基础机甲：'武装直升机小姐 - 空中支援，机动性强，可对地攻击。'",
        "characters": [
          {
            "name": "基础机甲",
            "image": "/uploads/images/scenes/characters/47982733-a03a-473a-8628-dcfec368a1a6.png",
            "position": "left"
          }
        ],
        "options": [
          {
            "text": "很好，开始部署！",
            "next": "defense_deploy"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "sceneKey": "defense_deploy",
      "content": {
        "bg": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1517649763962-0c623066050b?w=1920",
        "text": "各单位注意！指挥官下达部署命令！\n重型坦克和猛犸坦克负责正面防线，等离子坦克提供火力支援，武装直升机负责侦察和快速反应。",
        "characters": [
          {
            "name": "重型坦克",
            "image": "/uploads/images/scenes/characters/6757aca6-c7d4-44ee-94db-a98d7259f1ab.png",
            "position": "left"
          },
          {
            "name": "猛犸坦克",
            "image": "/uploads/images/scenes/characters/1d793dfa-f0de-4233-a9fe-60f40788bc7c.png",
            "position": "center"
          },
          {
            "name": "等离子坦克",
            "image": "/uploads/images/scenes/characters/02af157b-0dee-4205-81db-36f99dfab350.png",
            "position": "right"
          }
        ],
        "options": [
          {
            "text": "各单位报告状态",
            "next": "status_report"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "sceneKey": "status_report",
      "content": {
        "bg": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1517649763962-0c623066050b?w=1920",
        "text": "重型坦克：'重型坦克报告！主炮装填完毕，随时可以开火！'\n猛犸坦克：'猛犸坦克就位！我的装甲可以承受任何攻击！'\n等离子坦克：'等离子系统充能完成，等待射击指令。'",
        "characters": [
          {
            "name": "重型坦克",
            "image": "/uploads/images/scenes/characters/6757aca6-c7d4-44ee-94db-a98d7259f1ab.png",
            "position": "left"
          },
          {
            "name": "猛犸坦克",
            "image": "/uploads/images/scenes/characters/1d793dfa-f0de-4233-a9fe-60f40788bc7c.png",
            "position": "center"
          },
          {
            "name": "等离子坦克",
            "image": "/uploads/images/scenes/characters/02af157b-0dee-4205-81db-36f99dfab350.png",
            "position": "right"
          }
        ],
        "options": [
          {
            "text": "武装直升机，侦察情况如何？",
            "next": "heli_report"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "sceneKey": "heli_report",
      "content": {
        "bg": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1474302770737-173ee21bab63?w=1920",
        "text": "武装直升机：'报告指挥官！我从空中侦察到敌军动向！'\n武装直升机：'敌方大约有两个装甲连队正在向我方推进，预计十分钟后接触！'\n武装直升机：'另外，我发现敌军后方有一座能源设施，如果能够摧毁它，将大大削弱敌军战斗力！'",
        "characters": [
          {
            "name": "武装直升机",
            "image": "/uploads/images/scenes/characters/700aafa8-4e2a-4240-bc2d-d31c1d8e25ec.png",
            "position": "center"
          }
        ],
        "options": [
          {
            "text": "先防守基地，稳扎稳打",
            "next": "defensive_strategy"
          },
          {
            "text": "派遣突击队摧毁能源设施",
            "next": "offensive_strategy"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "sceneKey": "defensive_strategy",
      "content": {
        "bg": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1517649763962-0c623066050b?w=1920",
        "text": "指挥官决定采取防御策略！\n所有单位构筑防线，准备迎接敌军进攻！",
        "characters": [
          {
            "name": "重型坦克",
            "image": "/uploads/images/scenes/characters/6757aca6-c7d4-44ee-94db-a98d7259f1ab.png",
