    {
      "sceneKey": "mammoth_advance",
      "content": {
        "bg": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1517649763962-0c623066050b?w=1920",
        "text": "猛犸坦克：'明白！双管火炮，全速前进！'\n猛犸坦克如同一座移动堡垒，碾压过敌方防线！\n猛犸坦克：'没有人能阻挡我的前进！'",
        "characters": [
          {
            "name": "猛犸坦克",
            "image": "/uploads/images/scenes/characters/1d793dfa-f0de-4233-a9fe-60f40788bc7c.png",
            "position": "center"
          }
        ],
